description: Jared's second solo was the very next night and by this time Mike had sealed the deal. He knew exactly what he was going for next and 'post production planning' the night before seems to have opened some doors. He eases Jared right on into the next step and we get to sit back and enjoy this country boy bartering with the best of 'em and everyone coming out a winner in the end. We even get to enjoy him trying out a dildo!
title: Jared with a Dildo
